# clang-tidy is intentionally disabled for this repo.
#
# The previous broad profile made even small-looking translation units
# prohibitively slow because umbrella headers pull in Eigen, Arrow/Parquet,
# spdlog, SIMD, containers, concurrency, and stats. Keep verification on
# build warnings, tests, sanitizers where configured, and clang-format.
---
Checks: '-*'
WarningsAsErrors: ''
